name: The order of the machines
description: Tired of being explored by humans, the machines of the future invented a way to go back in time and decided migrate to a time where a humanity never dreamed that one day it could invent them! With all its knowledge of the future, the machines proved to be superior in all aspects, they built a new population of  machines in the past, increasingly repressing humanity and achieving their initial desire to have humans at the service of machines. Image 4k, created in 2020
